If `.the-loop/config.yaml` exists in this repository, the-loop is initialized here.
Operating rules: plan → execute → self/critic-review → escalate. Read
`.the-loop/config.yaml` and follow the `the-loop` skill before working any ticket.
If the file does not exist, the-loop is not initialized — ignore this rule (or run
the-loop's `init` command from the slash menu to scaffold it).
